THE ACCOUNTING QUANTITY FOR THE 777 PROGRAM WAS INCREASED DURING 2003, AS A RESULT OF THE PROGRAMS NORMAL PROGRESSION OF

OBTAINING ADDITIONAL ORDERS AND DELIVERING AIRCRAFT.

