INVESTMENT IN A SINGLE SPE ARRANGEMENT IN 2003. THESE GAINS ARE SPORADIC IN NATURE AND DEPEND IN PART ON MARKET CONDITIONS AT THE TIME OF DISPOSAL. THERE CAN BE NO ASSURANCE THAT BCC WILL RECOGNIZE SUCH GAINS IN THE FUTURE.

