EQUITY COMPENSATION PLAN INFORMATION

THE COMPANY CURRENTLY MAINTAINS FOUR EQUITY COMPENSATION PLANS THAT PROVIDE FOR THE ISSUANCE OF COMMON STOCK TO OFFICERS AND OTHER EMPLOYEES, DIRECTORS AND CONSULTANTS. EACH OF THESE COMPENSATION PLANS WAS APPROVED BY THE COMPANYS

SHAREHOLDERS. THE FOLLOWING TABLE SETS FORTH INFORMATION REGARDING OUTSTANDING OPTIONS AND SHARES AVAILABLE FOR FUTURE ISSUANCE UNDER THESE PLANS AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2003.

